@startuml
title VSLA Service Deployment Topology

node "Mobile Client" as Mobile {
    [Offline-First App]
}

node "VSLA Service Node" as VSLA_Node {
    package "Spring Boot" {
        [VSLA Application] as VSLA_App
        [Port 8081]
    }
    database "PostgreSQL" as VSLA_DB {
        [vsla_db schema]
    }
}

node "Fineract Core Node" as Fineract_Node {
    package "Spring Boot" {
        [Fineract Application] as Fineract_App
        [Port 8443]
    }
    database "PostgreSQL" as Fineract_DB {
        [fineract_db schema]
    }
}

Mobile --> VSLA_Node : HTTPS / REST / WebSocket
VSLA_Node --> Fineract_Node : HTTPS / REST
fineract-client
VSLA_App --> VSLA_DB : JDBC
Fineract_App --> Fineract_DB : JDBC

note right of VSLA_Node
  **No shared database**
  Loose coupling via REST only
end note

note right of Fineract_Node
  **Unmodified Fineract**
  Consumed via official
  Java REST API client
end note

@enduml
